Feel free to commit at will. pmurias is the author of all this. 
Visit #perl6 on freenode to flame him, or to get a commit bit from Audrey to help Pawel
with bringing parrot to the perl5 world.
Inline::Parrot uses nci for data exchange.
namespace.pir contains remains remains of a failed attempt at accessing parrot namespaces.
instead of perl5 ones. TIMTOWTDI I'm using nci now.
